<h2>quantdates: Manipulate Dates for Finance</h2>
<p>Functions to manipulate dates and count days for quantitative finance analysis. The 'quantdates' package considers leap, holidays and business days for relevant calendars in a financial context to simplify quantitative finance calculations, consistent with International Swaps and Derivatives Association (ISDA) (2006) &lt;<a href="https://www.isda.org/book/2006-isda-definitions/">https://www.isda.org/book/2006-isda-definitions/</a>&gt; regulations.</p>
